  <bioghist id="aspace_3002ceca8e28b73ccefbc5cc9e082e0f">
    <head>Historical/Biographical Note</head>
<p>John Gladstone was a member of the National Maritime Union and the Communist Party until 1949, when he was expelled from both organizations. He later became a publisher and editor at Engineer's Press, as well as an artist, and art historian.</p>  </bioghist>
